    <h1>Growth Loop</h1>
    <p class="description">A self-reinforcing system where the output of one cycle feeds directly into the input of the next — creating compounding growth without proportionally increasing spend. The framework that replaced the linear marketing funnel at companies like Slack, Pinterest, and Notion.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
